  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Melioidosis in head and neck was observed including clinical presentation, diagnosis with
      titer, and result of treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This research is retrospective study about five years ( Jan 2011- Oct 2016).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
